'''Jundland Pox''' was a disease that reportedly affected one in a million creatures on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]].

In [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]] the [[Bestine Hospital Medical Chief]] discovered an area of the planet that contained a higher than usual concentration of the disease. The Medical Chief hired hunters to significantly narrow the population of animals in that area to prevent further spread of the disease.

